      ></path>
    </svg>
    Save to GitHub
  </button>
</ExampleCard>

<ExampleCard
  title="Important icon without aria-hidden"
  description="❌ Icon that conveys important information but isn't hidden and lacks alternative text. Screen readers might announce confusing information or miss the meaning entirely."
>
  <div
    class="flex items-center gap-2 p-3 border border-red-300 dark:border-red-600 rounded bg-red-50 dark:bg-red-900/20"
  >
    <svg
      width="24"
      height="24"
      viewBox="0 0 20 20"
      fill="currentColor"
      class="text-red-600"
    >
      <path
        fill-rule="evenodd"
        d="M18 10a8 8 0 11-16 0 8 8 0 0116 0zm-7 4a1 1 0 11-2 0 1 1 0 012 0zm-1-9a1 1 0 00-1 1v4a1 1 0 102 0V6a1 1 0 00-1-1z"
        clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
    </svg>
    <span class="text-zinc-900 dark:text-zinc-100"
      >This is an error message</span
    >
  </div>
</ExampleCard>

<ExampleCard
  title="Accessible icon with proper labeling"
  description="✅ Icon that conveys meaning with proper accessible labeling using aria-label. The icon provides both visual and programmatic meaning."
>
  <div
    class="flex items-center gap-2 p-3 border border-green-300 dark:border-green-600 rounded bg-green-50 dark:bg-green-900/20"
  >
    <svg
      aria-label="Error"
      width="24"
      height="24"
      viewBox="0 0 20 20"
      fill="currentColor"
      class="text-red-600"
    >
      <path
        fill-rule="evenodd"
        d="M18 10a8 8 0 11-16 0 8 8 0 0116 0zm-7 4a1 1 0 11-2 0 1 1 0 012 0zm-1-9a1 1 0 00-1 1v4a1 1 0 102 0V6a1 1 0 00-1-1z"
        clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
    </svg>
    <span class="text-zinc-900 dark:text-zinc-100"
      >This is an error message</span
    >
  </div>
</ExampleCard>
